A scripting notebook for developers! Modify, adapt, convert in safety – now you can do it all!

- **Text editor** like [VS Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/).
- **Custom scripts** from `~/.textypie`.
- Optimized, lightweight, open source.

## Development

<details>

<summary>local development</summary>

### Tauri:

- Follow the instructions from [Tauri](https://v2.tauri.app/start/prerequisites/)

### Node

- Clone this repository
- Install latest LTS version of [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/en/)
- Enable [Corepack](https://github.com/nodejs/corepack) using `corepack enable`
- Install dependencies using `pnpm install`
- Run the application using `pnpm dev` as web
- Run the application using `pnpm dev:tauri` as app/web

</details>
